Cutting funding for the @WHO during a global pandemic is like cutting off our nose to spite our face. 

@realDonaldTrump: Pandemics don't respect borders. We need real leadership in galvanizing global action, not scapegoating for your own mistakes!
https://t.co/5WTk7a6QBQ

The last thing we need in the middle of a pandemic is regulatory rollbacks making it easier to build new natural gas pipelines.

@RepRaskin, @Ilhan &amp; I are calling on @FERC
 to halt approval &amp; construction of new natural gas pipelines to protect public participation &amp; health. https://t.co/76i88iXOau
